c: 6
v: 144
t: "Camels also [come] in twos and cattle in twos. SAY: \"Did He forbid both males or both females, or what both females´ wombs contain? Were you witnesses when God instructed you concerning this? Who does more harm than someone who invents a lie about God, so he may lead mankind astray without having any knowledge? God does not guide wrong-doing folk"